{
  "stem": "18770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of my memories which I have of that experience of coming to England-- I mean, sorry, coming to Canada is that the first day or two I think until we're put up somewhere else, we're staying in this little hotel.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they bring us breakfast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they bring out cereal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They bring out probably Kellogg's Flakes or something like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I, who had been raised with a chef-- I mean, with-- excuse me, with a guy-- with a cook who cooked like a chef, see these cornflakes in my plate.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I am tremendously impressed because I think each one of these has been made by hand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I think, God, this is fancy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "After all that running and living, you know, [LAUGHS] and we're eating these little handmade [LAUGHS] flakes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was my great first sort of introduction to Western eating.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We still-- it was still between-- now between the United States and South America.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're not going to stay in Canada.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think we can, probably.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we're not going to stay there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's a good-- I think it's looking more and more likely now that we will get into the United States.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we either have to wait for our visa number to come up or something to happen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know what that something is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I go to school there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you're starting to learn English?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Starting to learn English, wondering how all those kids speak this language.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that all the kids are geniuses because they all speak so quickly-- [LAUGHS] they speak this language.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we sing 'God Save the King' in school every morning and listen to the radio.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, but that's sort of-- that's the doorway to America.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
